* 科羅拉多州的[[比爾施塔特山|比爾施塔特山]]和[[比爾施塔特湖|比爾施塔特湖]]都是以其名字命名的。此外他還可能是最早登頂落基山脈比爾施塔特山不遠處的[[埃爾斯山|埃爾斯山]]的歐洲人。<ref>William Newton Byers, Bierstadt's Visit to Colorado: Sketching for the famous painting ''Storm in the Rocky Mountains'', [http://books.google.com/books?id=4fMOAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA238-IA5 Magazine of Western History] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=4fMOAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA238-IA5 |date=20200725021652 }}, Vol. XI, No. 3, Jan. 1890; page 237.</ref>  其實原來此山由比爾施塔特取名為羅莎山（Mount Rosa），此名來自瑞士的[[罗莎峰|罗莎峰]]和他未來的妻子羅莎莉·勒德洛（Rosalie Ludlow）。
* 1998年，[[美國郵政管理局|美國郵政管理局]]發行了一套20枚的郵票，題為“Four Centuries of American Art”（美國藝術四百年），其中包含比爾施塔特的畫作《The Last of the Buffalo》。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.artonstamps.org/Countries/USA/USArt-400.htm |title=ArtOnStamps.org |publisher=ArtOnStamps.org |date=2010-07-09 |accessdate=2012-05-20 |archive-date=2017-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171109060704/http://www.artonstamps.org/Countries/USA/USArt-400.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>  2008年此機構發行的另一套郵票“American Treasures”（美國珍寶）則包含比爾施塔特1864年的作品《Valley of the Yosemite》<ref>{{cite web |url=http://shop.usps.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/ProductDisplay?catalogId=10152&storeId=10001&categoryId=21902&productId=39451&langId=-1 |title=The Postal Store @ USPS.com |publisher=Shop.usps.com |date=2011-03-28 |accessdate=2012-05-20 |archive-date=2009-02-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090221132552/http://shop.usps.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/ProductDisplay?catalogId=10152&storeId=10001&categoryId=21902&productId=39451&langId=-1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，此畫在1995年電影《[[十二隻猴子|十二隻猴子]]》中也有出現。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.xmission.com/~emailbox/glenda/bierstadt/b-valley_of_the_yosemite.jpg |title=image of Valley of the Yosemite |accessdate=2012-12-19 |archive-date=2011-06-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110605192516/http://www.xmission.com/~emailbox/glenda/bierstadt/b-valley_of_the_yosemite.jpg |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0114746/trivia |title=Twelve Monkeys trivia page at IMDB |access-date=2014-11-08 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129004147/https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0114746/trivia |dead-url=no }}</ref>

